Class PlantUmlTextGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nasdanika.emf.PlantUmlTextGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DiagramTextGenerator
    public class PlantUmlTextGenerator
extends Object
implements DiagramTextGenerator
    Generates PlantUML text from Ecore models. This code is based on net.sourceforge.plantuml.text.AbstractDiagramTextProvider and net.sourceforge.plantuml.ecore.AbstractEcoreDiagramTextProvider from https://github.com/hallvard/plantuml
    Author:
    Pavel Vlasov
